data.title: Awn website mockup (2009/09/16)
data.meta_description:
In this update, I've added JQuery support, which includes an emulation of the following dock features:
	 * a "bounce" effect when you hover over a navigation icon
	 * a per-navigation icon translucent tooltip
	
	I have also added two pseudo-buttons to distinctly show two important links: how to install Awn, and getting help for Awn.
	
	I forgot to note in the last screenshot that the entire site is written using the HTML5 spec.
	
	As with the last screenshot, it is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 (unported) license.
data.text:
In this update, I've added JQuery support, which includes an emulation of the following dock features:

* a "bounce" effect when you hover over a navigation icon

* a per-navigation icon translucent tooltip

I have also added two pseudo-buttons to distinctly show two important links: how to install Awn, and getting help for Awn.

I forgot to note in the last screenshot that the entire site is written using the HTML5 spec.

As with the last screenshot, it is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 (unported) license.
